          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/56445988/" class=" " title="君子不欺公子方">君子不欺公子方</a>
                (奕生侍臣。)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="23152997">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">世俗之人，皆喜人之同乎己，而恶人之异于己也。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-12-13 23:18</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">7人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                世俗之人，皆喜人之同乎己，而恶人之异于己也。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
